  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/2116f0084f22aaae5997dfee40897248.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to War Islands! A third-person cooperative action-adventure game full of mysteries and magical experiences. Team up to 3 players <strong>online</strong> or in <strong>local split screen</strong> engaging in thrilling battles as you progress through an enchanting storyline. Whether you're solving puzzles, facing formidable foes, or discovering new realms, embark on an unforgettable journey brimming with secrets and challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE A NEW WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/6b1caa636a7f67e080733d4e76be1b36.poster.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/6b1caa636a7f67e080733d4e76be1b36.webm?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/6b1caa636a7f67e080733d4e76be1b36.mp4?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across a landscape full of intrigue. From a whimsical forest, where magic comes alive, to a deep dark cave, home to a host of nightmarish creatures.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEAT BEASTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/db2fff9b8e34cbea6776a815a8a53e83.poster.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/db2fff9b8e34cbea6776a815a8a53e83.webm?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/db2fff9b8e34cbea6776a815a8a53e83.mp4?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slash, shoot, conjure spells and fight your way through fearsome beasts to free and unify the inhabitants of War Islands.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAT CHALLENGING PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/eaf9418c5c776a03d62c4108ac2b08ea.poster.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/eaf9418c5c776a03d62c4108ac2b08ea.webm?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/eaf9418c5c776a03d62c4108ac2b08ea.mp4?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Integrate your characters unique abilities to overcome intricate puzzles, designed around a cooperative experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/9431fc7b3835d511cf938a375eb4b507.poster.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/9431fc7b3835d511cf938a375eb4b507.webm?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/9431fc7b3835d511cf938a375eb4b507.mp4?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock skills to empower your heroes and combine their powers for maximum combat synergy. Discover items throughout the world to enhance your stats as you progress through the story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HELP THE GUINEA PIGS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/8df4c829e4f0c36ffb6cec653adebc2a.poster.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/8df4c829e4f0c36ffb6cec653adebc2a.webm?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/8df4c829e4f0c36ffb6cec653adebc2a.mp4?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unfold the history of the native guinea pigs and help them reconquer their islands back from the evil paws of Nekomata: The Villainess Cat Leader!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/2116f0084f22aaae5997dfee40897248.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to War Islands! A third-person cooperative action-adventure game full of mysteries and magical experiences. Team up to 3 players <strong>online</strong> or in <strong>local split screen</strong> engaging in thrilling battles as you progress through an enchanting storyline. Whether you're solving puzzles, facing formidable foes, or discovering new realms, embark on an unforgettable journey brimming with secrets and challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE A NEW WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/6b1caa636a7f67e080733d4e76be1b36.poster.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/6b1caa636a7f67e080733d4e76be1b36.webm?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/6b1caa636a7f67e080733d4e76be1b36.mp4?t=1759667035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across a landscape full of intrigue. From a whimsical forest, where magic comes alive, to a deep dark cave, home to a host of nightmarish creatures.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEAT BEASTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268100/extras/db2fff9b8e34cbea6776a815a8a53e83.poster.avif?t=1759667035\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto